lead_paragraph: German Stephan Jaeger completed a historical first when he shot a 12-under-par 58 on the PGA Tour's secondary Web.com Tour in California on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: German Jaeger Shoots Record-Breaking 58 on Web.com Tour
